                  <span class="c00">I don&#x27;t have a Twitter account but occasionally arrive on that site through a link.<p>I concur with the author that retweets are lazy noise.  And quite often they reveal aspects of a person&#x27;s character that I&#x27;d rather not know.<p>Maybe Twitter would be better if it had a technical means of enforcing only original thought.  Perhaps some day in the AI future...<span>
